Package RestaurantSim

Class Restaurant

java.lang.Object
RestaurantSim.Restaurant
All Implemented Interfaces:
ITickableActionObject
public class Restaurant
extends java.lang.Object
implements ITickableActionObject
A class that resembles a Restaurant. It is the heart of the simulation. Restaurant has cooks that make orders requested by RestaurantGuests, returns prepared orders to proper guests, interacts with guests that are waiting in its queue, also manages them. Restaurant can be rated by any RestaurantGuest and closed by object of Sanepid type.

    • receiveOrderRequest

      public OrderReceipt receiveOrderRequest​(Order order, float payForOrder)
      Receives an order request and if restaurant is able to handle it this function will return an OrderReceipt object.
      Parameters:
      order - Order to make
      payForOrder - Total payment for the requested order. If it's less than required sum of prices of all ingredients this function will not process the request and return null.
      Returns:
      OrderReceipt or null if request couldn't be processed.
